{"tid":2354103,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★奴工處周四起舉辦2日網上招聘會 提供大量1萬元至2萬元荀工！","createTime":"2021-01-05T08:19:00.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-05T14:41:32.000Z","uid":19454,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"41e12420031852c28624e41362f6b2172c5db1a4","tid":2354103,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T08:19:00.000Z","msg":"勞工處表示，將於周四（7日）至周五（8日）下午6時，在該處互動就業服務網站（<a href=\"http://www.jobs.gov.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.jobs.gov.hk&d=QL2FFPepynYtbGyOTzoAGyL1bdbhbSvxCnYHZ8iA0HE%3D&h=021aa237\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.jobs.gov.hk</a>）舉辦職場創新機網上招聘會，讓求職人士瀏覽職位空缺資料及遞交網上求職申請。招聘會共有44間機構參加，主要來自商用服務、物業管理及零售業，合共提供超過2,500個職位空缺。<br />\n   <br />\n參與機構提供的職位類別包括客戶服務主任、會計文員、行政助理、數碼市務主任、動物領養助理、寵物美容師、小學學習班導師、健身教練、烹飪助理、技術員及工程師等。當中約79%為全職空缺，<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>大部分月薪介乎1萬元至2萬元</strong></span>；約98%的職位空缺學歷要求為中六或以下，約75%的職位空缺無需相關工作經驗。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2844484/%E5%8B%9E%E5%B7%A5%E8%99%95%E5%91%A8%E5%9B%9B%E8%B5%B7%E8%88%89%E8%BE%A62%E6%97%A5%E7%B6%B2%E4%B8%8A%E6%8B%9B%E8%81%98%E6%9C%83%20%20%20%20%E6%8F%90%E4%BE%9B2,500%E5%80%8B%E8%81%B7%E4%BD%8D%E7%A9%BA%E7%BC%BA?mtc=10012\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2844484%2F%25E5%258B%259E%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E8%2599%2595%25E5%2591%25A8%25E5%259B%259B%25E8%25B5%25B7%25E8%2588%2589%25E8%25BE%25A62%25E6%2597%25A5%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E4%25B8%258A%25E6%258B%259B%25E8%2581%2598%25E6%259C%2583%2520%2520%2520%2520%25E6%258F%2590%25E4%25BE%259B2%2C500%25E5%2580%258B%25E8%2581%25B7%25E4%25BD%258D%25E7%25A9%25BA%25E7%25BC%25BA%3Fmtc%3D10012&d=QL2FFPepynYtbGyOTzoAGyL1bdbhbSvxCnYHZ8iA0HE%3D&h=cb44b4b8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2844484/%E5%8B%9E%E5%B7%A5%E8%99%95%E5%91%A8%E5%9B%9B%E8%B5%B7%E8%88%89%E8%BE%A62%E6%97%A5%E7%B6%B2%E4%B8%8A%E6%8B%9B%E8%81%98%E6%9C%83%20%20%20%20%E6%8F%90%E4%BE%9B2,500%E5%80%8B%E8%81%B7%E4%BD%8D%E7%A9%BA%E7%BC%BA?mtc=10012</a>"},{"pid":"8e010ef357bdfadcc6c1a2e695a02eea8f062e8f","tid":2354103,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T08:19:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19b26d39bdf0c54a6b63de85cbb4adae9c2de760","tid":2354103,"uid":127905,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T08:19:55.000Z","msg":"申謮公屋唔過入息<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fec5688de41e956cb71c6e12693b0a8271c2f68","tid":2354103,"uid":48161,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T08:19:57.000Z","msg":"周綺萍：咁撚高既<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b320f625c599876925b780479f778bf9fd11e1b8","tid":2354103,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T08:20:01.000Z","msg":"50k Lihkg仔表示：<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c554ec06430be84ad1e6aa29fbdfcea63365142c","tid":2354103,"uid":86509,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T08:20:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/09/110551_60ba4eff1cc0daa225d85f725df5b946.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F09%2F110551_60ba4eff1cc0daa225d85f725df5b946.jpg&h=d183e30a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a25ef72d7c1a0076a1fc