www.jobs.gov.hk&d=QL2FFPepynYtbGyOTzoAGyL1bdbhbSvxCnYHZ8iA0HE%3D&h=021aa237\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.jobs.gov.hk</a>）舉辦職場創新機網上招聘會，讓求職人士瀏覽職位空缺資料及遞交網上求職申請。招聘會共有44間機構參加，主要來自商用服務、物業管理及零售業，合共提供超過2,500個職位空缺。<br />\n   <br />\n參與機構提供的職位類別包括客戶服務主任、會計文員、行政助理、數碼市務主任、動物領養助理、寵物美容師、小學學習班導師、健身教練、烹飪助理、技術員及工程師等。當中約79%為全職空缺，<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>大部分月薪介乎1萬元至2萬元</strong></span>；約98%的職位空缺學歷要求為中六或以下，約75%的職位空缺無需相關工作經驗。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2844484/%E5%8B%9E%E5%B7%A5%E8%99%95%E5%91%A8%E5%9B%9B%E8%B5%B7%E8%88%89%E8%BE%A62%E6%97%A5%E7%B6%B2%E4%B8%8A%E6%8B%9B%E8%81%98%E6%9C%83%20%20%20%20%E6%8F%90%E4%BE%9B2,500%E5%80%8B%E8%81%B7%E4%BD%8D%E7%A9%BA%E7%BC%BA?mtc=10012\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2844484%2F%25E5%258B%259E%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E8%2599%2595%25E5%2591%25A8%25E5%259B%259B%25E8%25B5%25B7%25E8%2588%2589%25E8%25BE%25A62%25E6%2597%25A5%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E4%25B8%258A%25E6%258B%259B%25E8%2581%2598%25E6%259C%2583%2520%2520%2520%2520%25E6%258F%2590%25E4%25BE%259B2%2C500%25E5%2580%258B%25E8%2581%25B7%25E4%25BD%258D%25E7%25A9%25BA%25E7%25BC%25BA%3Fmtc%3D10012&d=QL2FFPepynYtbGyOTzoAGyL1bdbhbSvxCnYHZ8iA0HE%3D&h=cb44b4b8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2844484/%E5%8B%9E%E5%B7%A5%E8%99%95%E5%91%A8%E5%9B%9B%E8%B5%B7%E8%88%89%E8%BE%A62%E6%97%A5%E7%B6%B2%E4%B8%8A%E6%8B%9B%E8%81%98%E6%9C%83%20%20%20%20%E6%8F%90%E4%BE%9B2,500%E5%80%8B%E8%81%B7%E4%BD%8D%E7%A9%BA%E7%BC%BA?mtc=10012</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T13:39:10.000Z","msg":"2萬算多"},{"pid":"d0c51ca7bfacc562435c7d6e45e227b0f5bb1067","tid":2354103,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T14:36:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img 